name: Chill Bone
description: A simple yet stylish skull that embodies a laid-back and carefree vibe. Dressed in a cozy pink hoodie against a vibrant blue background, this character exudes a mix of innocence and mystery. With its large, round, deep eyes and a tiny skeletal nose, it has an effortlessly cool and minimalistic appeal. A perfect blend of casual and spooky, making it a standout piece in any collection.
